AD DS Setup.

Add Roles and Features Wizard > Next > Role Based Or Feature based Installation > Next > 
Select a Server from the server pool > Next > Check Mark(Active Directory Domain Service) >
Add Features > Next > Next > Next > Install.

Promote to Domain Controller.

From Notification bar > click Promote this Server to a Domain Controller > Add a new Forest(From 
add a new forest Give a name to Root Domain name) > Next > Give Password > Next > Next > Next > 
Next > Next > Install > PC will restart and Installation will complete.
